social_posts.post_text: Love using my ilevel for transfers! Excited that it is warm enough to go cruising.
I love getting fresh ingredients from my garden to cook with!

The last couple weeks have had some magical moments. 
Happy wedding to my beautiful niece! And a few other fun moments. Even though there have been a couple hard things, mostly it’s been beautiful!

Life is beautiful if you let it be. This is one of the most wholesome moments I’ve ever been apart of. Thank you to all that let me be apart of this. #doutah #do_utah #disabledoutdoorsmen #wholesome #beautiful

free·dom
/ˈfrēdəm/
noun
the power or right to act, speak, or think as one wants without hindrance or restraint.

I think that we forget how powerful the word freedom is. I’ve always been one that doesn’t want to be held back. I’ve always wanted to explore and be adventurous. I’ve always wanted to go and see the world without restraint. Once I got my first power chair I realized how much freedom I could have. I’ve been driving a smaller car that was more affordable. I usually have to take my manual chair apart. Or have someone with me. Truthfully it’s been hard on my body. With this van I can roll right in and go wherever I want. 
Freedom. Don’t underestimate the power of it. 

Thank you again for changing my life and opening my world. 
@do_utah 
@compassionmobility 
@suregriphc 
📸 @peakedoutadventures

My daughter and I are a team. It’s always been the 2 of us against the world.  And now because of the kindness of @do_utah and @compassionmobility we can see more of the world. We can take my @quantum_rehab chair on more  adventures than i can ever imagine. My heart is so full.

Just over here doing my new van dance! #quantumrehab #4front2 #wheelchairlife #accessiblevehicles 
So grateful to @do_utah for changing my life!

happy Friday!! I love that I’m able to take my @quantum_rehab power chair to work now! It’s so convenient and it’s easier on my body!#wheelchairlife #fyp #arhrogryposis #quantumrehab #4front2 #amcawareness
Peace.
Happy Father’s Day dad.
Cruising around at the Ogden farmers market was a good time!!#wheelchairlife #fyp #arhrogryposis #quantumrehab #4front2 #freedom

What do you do when you can go anywhere you want? I went to @target and pushed my own shopping cart at ilevel! It’s pretty fun to argue with my kid about who gets to push the cart! And of course we got @starbucks !!#wheelchairlife #fyp #arhrogryposis #quantumrehab #4front2
@tanfrance  and I showing  off our fancy boots at the @kelseaballerini show last night!

We got tickets to see @taylorswift with our besties in LA! Can’t wait till Aug 7!

#quantumrehab #4front2 #taylorswifterastour #goingbacktocali

I love that my power chair makes getting outside so easy! I love being in the mountains and sunshine with my people. 
#quantumrehab #4front2 #wheelchairlife
I love the freedom I have to get out and see this beautiful world! #amcawareness #disabilitypride #fyp #wheelchairlife #quantumrehab #4front2 #freedom #arhrogryposis

When i tell you my power chair has given me freedom… i pumped my own gas!!
I have always needed help until now. Getting my manual chair in and out t took longer than asking for help. Now i can do it quick and easy!! 

It’s little things that make me happy. I love how much freedom i have!!#amcawareness #disabilitypride #fyp #quantumrehab #4front2
I love going to the lake! #quantumrehab #4front2
Can’t wait to see Taylor!! #tsxcapitalone #sweetskapes

Absolute magic! @taylorswift didn’t disappoint! I can’t believe we got to experience this! Moments like this will never be forgotten. We laughed and cried! We most definitely sang our hearts out!

Thank you to the girls behind us for capturing this!
I will never forget this!
I will sing All Too Well 10 minute version with you every time! You are my best friend and greatest joy. This experience was incredible.

My brother lived here for years. This is where he had his wedding. The damage is extensive and and people we know and love have lost so much. If you can help please Venmo. 
https://account.venmo.com/u/robertw87
Any little bit would help.
I sure love summer! It’s always great to find an accessible pool:) #quantumrehab #4front2
How has she grown up so fast! My lil @londonlovesswift started high school today!

We spent a beautiful morning picking flowers with @londonlovesswift  on an incredible farm! I loved it! Can’t wait to go back to @onceuponachristmastreefarm ! #4front2 #fyp #quantumrehab #wheelchairlife #arhrogryposis
Happy birthday to my momma! My ride or die!
A little birthday eve witchery! Excited for the super moon tonight! #witchaesthetic #simmerpot #supermoon

A moon ceremony for my birthday was pretty magical… i was so happy to realize the super blue moon landed on my 41st! We made absolute magic! #witch #witchcraft #witchythings #witchtok #fyp #supermoon #birthdaygirl #wheelchairlife #birthdaygirl
When its time to unload the car just load me up!!#fyp #wheelchairlife #arhrogryposis #4front2 #quantumrehab

This week I’ve really been thinking about fall.  Usually i hate when summer is over. I don’t like when the chill in the air starts. But this year I’ve been thinking about how beautiful it is to embrace that change. 
Trees change. They let go. Every year. I can embrace that too. 
#fyp #wheelchairlife #arhrogryposis #4front2 #quantumrehab #freedom

A year ago I was in Peru. This trip with @chairthehope 💯 changed my life. It brought me closer to my daughter. It showed me how see the magic in the smallest moments. This trip brought me back to life 🥹#fyp #wheelchairlife #wheelchairtravel #wheelchairmom #peru #chairthehope
Few people come into your world and make it infinitely better… love you bestie. Happy Birthday!!! @christinafamilylife
I love seeing my people in love. What an  honor to officiate your wedding. I’m so proud of both of you!
2023, you were good to me.
